data.description: A Rare Gem in Washington Park: A Golden Investment Opportunity Awaits You!    Nestled just five minutes away from the world-renowned University of Chicago and the prestigious Booth School of Business, this cash-flowing, 4-unit solid brick property is not just a building; it's a real estate trophy. Add it to your portfolio, or make it your very own home.    Just imagine owning a property where each unit stands as a symbol of modern luxury. With three spacious bedrooms and two elegant bathrooms, the comforts of contemporary living merge seamlessly with classic appeal. The beautiful hardwood floors glisten under natural light, and the open floor plan breathes life into each unit.    Each unit is complete with its own washer and dryer, providing an unmatched level of convenience and modern amenity that is truly rare in Washington Park.    Entertaining and relaxation have never been so effortless. Picture yourself enjoying a morning coffee on your charming Juliet balcony or bedazzling guests while grilling culinary delights on your private outdoor deck. With a generous living space adorned with a fireplace and a separate dining area, your happy tenants will relish every moment spent at home.    This investment is more than just a property; it's a lifestyle opportunity. Whether you are an aspiring "house hacker", and Airbnb entreperneur, or a seasoned investor in search of a well-maintained, cash-flowing opportunity, this deal is tailor-made for your success. With dedicated private parking for each unit, convenience meets luxury on this magnificent property.    This is a rare chance to invest in a world-class property promising substantial reward potential. Schedule your appointment today, and prepare to take possession of this gem in beautiful Washington Park.
